Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Reside at historic Thomas Park, where history intersects with modern elegance. Ideally located in a highly walkable area, 75 G is a collection of three distinctive residences that have been thoughtfully designed to preserve the charm of a historical home while offering the advantages of new construction. Unit 1 enjoys two personal entrances with Blink camera doorbell, deeded off-street parking and a beautiful private fenced in terrace. As you step inside, you are welcomed by a sun-drenched, open-concept layout accentuated by white oak floors, high ceilings, ample windows, and a chef’s kitchen complete with custom cabinets, Thermador appliances and Quartz countertops. Flexible layouts include main-level bedrooms and lower-level suites. Additional perks include in-unit laundry, spa-like bathrooms and central air. Live just steps from miles of shoreline and all the shops and restaurants Broadway has to offer ensuring you experience the best of South Boston living!
